item.title: TESTIMONAILS
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: [vc_row box_padding="padding-100"][vc_column][vc_single_testimonial image="4956" author="FATOMA HASSAN"]Friends from Utica recommended Joey's Restaurant, so we drove down one evening for dinner. We can't say enough good things about our experience.[/vc_single_testimonial][vc_single_testimonial image="4956" author="FATOMA HASSAN"]We've been to Joey's many times over the years. We know what to expect: great food and great prices. I suggest checking them out.[/vc_single_testimonial][vc_single_testimonial image="4956" author="TOUFA GAMAA"]I can't say enough about your quaint Italian Restaurant! The reasonable prices, and great atmosphere are only topped by the delicious food.[/vc_single_testimonial][vc_single_testimonial image="4956" author="AMANY ARAFA"]Joey's is simply the BEST there is! Great Food, big portions, nice atmosphere.[/vc_single_testimonial][vc_single_testimonial image="4956" author="LOLA HASSAN"]We love Joey's. Over the last 4 years, we've sampled almost everything on the menu and often order the listed daily specials.[/vc_single_testimonial][/vc_column][/vc_row]
